{"tid":2366012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(分析) 點解連尼往 一直唔bam 五毛/打手/PR","createTime":"2021-01-14T07:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T09:27:28.000Z","uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"46b076cc31dfcb39a71b48f9c086548811dd820a","tid":2366012,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:41:43.000Z","msg":"香港編年史 比共產黨 bam左, 即係話佢地有能力向連登開刀<br />\n如果bam晒五毛, 等於同共產黨反面, 到時就逼到佢地直接封網<br />\n連登既存在 等於以前香港 係中國既角色<br />\n共產黨可以係連登用五毛吹風, 但冇左連登五毛就地方去搞分化<br />\n連登有五毛會影響討論,但冇左連登 我地就要去第二度,好難再有咁多人既討論區<br />\n而家連登 五毛活躍, 連住尼唔bam, 由得佢地, 起碼共產黨唔會急住封連登,大家可能再玩多1,2年<br />\n<br />\n所以呢個現象 算係連狗同共產黨 妥協下既產物, 大家隻眼開隻眼閉,好來好去,<br />\n廢時步而家香港後塵,搞到攬抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4fb8f4713254ccbe7faffa4530290261e3d9ea","tid":2366012,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"[置頂] LIHKG 常見問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1660096\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1660096</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔打分析兩隻字都冇咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61454637b8762b096893ec24889a7baca0cbf6ab","tid":2366012,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f709811f4fa26560c2d4e2bc311c4a0a84672e8b","tid":2366012,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:51:55.000Z","msg":"你點知佢獨資定合資<br />\n<br />\n人地都冇表態  當一個平台者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5789bcaa6b09180305bd69419b0b894a0a4b857e","tid":2366012,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d4fb8f4713254ccbe7faffa4530290261e3d9ea","tid":2366012,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"[置頂] LIHKG